  "text": "Find GCC GIMPLE pass patterns to implement a minimal GIMPLE pass. Find: 1. pass_data struct and gimple_opt_pass class definition in gcc/tree-pass.h (lines 40-123) -- the base types every GIMPLE pass inherits. 2. gate() and execute() virtual methods on opt_pass (tree-pass.h lines 90-96). 3. Complete worked example in gcc/tree-ssa-dce.cc: pass_data_dce, pass_dce_base (extends gimple_opt_pass with gate/execute), pass_dce, and make_pass_dce() factory. 4. dump_file usage in tree-ssa-dce.cc for diagnostic output during pass execution. 5. passes.def NEXT_PASS(pass_dce) entries showing how passes are registered in the pipeline.",
